The paper discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for automatic target recognition (ATR) in Sonar imagery, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions transfer learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper proposes a method for target detection and identification, which is related to robotics (cs.RO).
